://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x143_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。类似于情形1.2.1的证法，我们可以得证<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x144_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x145_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，我们在圈<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x146_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>选择一条边<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x147_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>使得<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x148_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。类似于情形1.1.2的证法，我们可以得到<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x149_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>情形1.2.4. 图<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x150_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>中不含圈长为4的圈。类似于情形1.1.3的证法，当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x151_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，结论成立。</p><p>假定<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x152_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x153_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，对于任意的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x154_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>阶有向双圈图<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x155_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/1-2620166x156_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></